            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Herennio <lb n="3"/>Tromentina Valenti <lb n="4"/>Salona evocato <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XI <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiae</ex></expan> |(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eiusd</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>|(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> |(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>|(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> |(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>iteru</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>I <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> |(centurioni) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> V <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">ha</supplied>st</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>post</abbr><ex>eriori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> LV <lb n="10"/>vixit annis LXXV <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Herennius Helius <lb n="12"/>libertus et heres <lb n="13"/>patrono <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciundum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> <lb n="14"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>oc</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>onumentum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eredem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>on</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>equetur</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld von Pilastern eingefasst; darüber Tierfries mit jagenden Hunden, Hirsch und Hase; über dem Fries ein Bildfeld mit der Büste eines centurio, die von den Figuren zweier junger Männer (Diener?) flankiert wird. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): CIL 03, 13360; Schober; Fitz: geringfügige Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
